  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6314069">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6314069/" class="title-link">窥得一片新天地</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6314069"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/longs/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1719574-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/longs/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">龙九天</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-10-05"
      class="main-meta">2013-10-05 13:32:39</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6314069_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  不知道是谁说过，世界由圈子组成。娱乐明星有娱乐圈，学者有学者圈，商人有商圈。圈外的人好奇圈内的生活。任志强名声之大、地位之显，不知有多少人好奇想了解他所在圈子的隐私生活。《野心优雅——任志强回忆录》披露了大量的交易内幕、私密生活。正如他在书中所言：我写这部...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">11有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
